103 però che ’l ben, ch’è del volere obietto, 104 tutto s’accoglie in lei, e fuor di quella 105 è defettivo ciò ch’è lì perfetto.

query.result:
**English:**
100 In that light one becomes such 101 that to turn away from it to another aspect 102 is impossible, and consent is never granted;
103 because the good, which is the object of desire, 104 is all gathered in it, and outside of it 105 that which is perfect there is defective.
**Sanskrit:**
