**Sanskrit:**
115 Gambhīrāyām ca sphaṭikāyām sthitau 116 Jyotiṣaḥ parāt tridhā bhramaṇāni me adṛśyanta 117 Trivarṇāni ca ekatvātmakāni ca;
118 Ekaṃ ca anyasmāt iva cakrāṇi cakrāt 119 Pratīkāśam iva adṛśyata, tṛtīyaṃ tu iva agniḥ 120 Yaḥ iha ca amutra ca samam iva praśvasiti.
